thread.title: Elaine Reading
thread.title_full: CEWE Photoworld reviewed by Elaine Reading

author: Elaine Reading
title: Elaine Reading
text: The quality of the photo book I made for my boyfriend is excellent. I was a little apprehensive as it was the first one I've made & it was a bit of a rush, but the paper and the hardback cover are just what I wanted and the colours and definition on the photos are perfect. Very pleased - so will have to find time to do mine next!
